rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Many customer come from across
Alst to buy all kind of things here
at Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
But that not only people that
come to Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Bad people also come. Steal things
from customers while they distracted
by shopping.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Friends make sure keep bag closed
tight, so nobody steal things inside!

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If friends see suspicious persons,
please report to Rimurimu!
